originalText.text: I have been in search of the right fit, to pivot my career, As a nurse my goal is and will always be to make sure that my patients/clients are cared for in a way that is not only professional but genuine. I met my match with Anita... Her knowledge, her skills , her ability to help you find your zone, is beyond words. I know I could have gone else where, but you wouldn't possibly get the intimate, one on one training that you want and need as you move forward into this amazing field! Ill be back for the guidance of an Expert... and I'm not using that term lightly. This is the real deal!! Thanks Anita and Carolina for such an awesome experience!

originalText.text:
I had an incredible experience at BeautyFix Training Center in New York City. The Beginner BOTOX and Dermal Filler Course exceeded my expectations. The classes are well-structured, with a comprehensive lecture and hands-on practice on live models. Anita Wolf, our trainer, was exceptional. Her expertise and passion for teaching were evident throughout the course.
I gained valuable insights into facial anatomy, learned about the science of botulinum toxin and dermal fillers, and even received guidance on managing complications. The hands-on practice allowed me to inject different areas with Botox and dermal fillers, including cheeks, chin, and lips. The small group setting ensured personalized attention, making me feel confident as I started injecting my first patients.
Anita’s extensive experience as an injectable trainer truly shone through. Her expertise in the field, having taught various procedures to professionals across the country, was evident in her teaching style. The 24/7 access to course materials was a great resource for further learning.
I highly recommend the BeautyFix Training Center to both beginners and experienced practitioners. Whether you're entering the field or looking to enhance your skills, this course offers a fantastic learning experience led by top professionals like Anita. Special thanks to Carolina and the entire team for creating an environment that fosters growth and learning. This training has given me an edge as I step into the world of medical aesthetics.
